      "start_time": 332796.0,
      "end_time": 334635.0,
      "text": "we can add them as a separate component."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 334635.0,
      "end_time": 336635.0,
      "text": "We can keep the ScoreText selected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 336635.0,
      "end_time": 339921.0,
      "text": "go to Add Component and just type the word Shadow"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 339922.0,
      "end_time": 341922.0,
      "text": "and it will immediately find that component"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 341922.0,
      "end_time": 343922.0,
      "text": "and you can hit Return."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 344772.0,
      "end_time": 346257.0,
      "text": "That will just give you a slight drop shadow."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 346257.0,
      "end_time": 348257.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to make it a bit more obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 348257.0,
      "end_time": 354143.0,
      "text": "by changing the Effect Distance to 2, -2 in the X and Y axis."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 355659.0,
      "end_time": 357659.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also important to keep that"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 357659.0,
      "end_time": 359460.0,
      "text": "Use Graphic Alpha checked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 359470.0,
      "end_time": 361288.0,
      "text": "otherwise if you change the alpha"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 361288.0,
      "end_time": 364103.0,
      "text": "of the text the shadow won&#39;t also change."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 364885.0,
      "end_time": 366885.0,
      "text": "What you&#39;ll notice about this is if I change the"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 366885.0,
      "end_time": 368885.0,
      "text": "alpha of the text itself the shadow"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 368885.0,
      "end_time": 370885.0,
      "text": "underneath is also fading out."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 370885.0,
      "end_time": 372885.0,
      "text": "Whereas if it&#39;s not checked"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 373207.0,
      "end_time": 374825.0,
      "text": "we can fade this and then the shadow"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 374825.0,
      "end_time": 377732.0,
      "text": "will get left behind which is not desirable."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 379800.0,
      "end_time": 381800.0,
      "text": "And then we need something to set"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 381800.0,
      "end_time": 383800.0,
      "text": "the score, something to be managing"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 383800.0,
      "end_time": 386370.0,
      "text": "the score, updating the text component&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 386370.0,
      "end_time": 388522.0,
      "text": "text value with Score 10, Score 20,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 388522.0,
      "end_time": 390522.0,
      "text": "whatever happens in the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 390522.0,
      "end_time": 392522.0,
      "text": "And the way that we&#39;re going to do this is"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 392522.0,
      "end_time": 394522.0,
      "text": "by adding a Manager script."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 394522.0,
      "end_time": 396522.0,
      "text": "So what I&#39;d like you to do is look in"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 396522.0,
      "end_time": 399205.0,
      "text": "the Scripts - Managers folder"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 399205.0,
      "end_time": 402691.0,
      "text": "and you will find out Score Manager."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 402691.0,
      "end_time": 404691.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to drag and drop this on to the"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 404691.0,
      "end_time": 407610.0,
      "text": "ScoreText game object"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 409322.0,
      "end_time": 411322.0,
      "text": "Then once you&#39;ve applied it you should see"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 411322.0,
      "end_time": 413844.0,
      "text": "it at the bottom of the list of components"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 414356.0,
      "end_time": 415851.0,
      "text": "right underneath the shadow"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 415851.0,
      "end_time": 417851.0,
      "text": "and we can double click to open that up."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 419172.0,
      "end_time": 421998.0,
      "text": "So at the start we again have our public variables."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 421998.0,
      "end_time": 424521.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll notice there&#39;s a new keyword there"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 424521.0,
      "end_time": 426950.0,
      "text": "Static."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 426950.0,
      "end_time": 430207.0,
      "text": "So a static variable doesn&#39;t belong to the instance"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 430207.0,
      "end_time": 433435.0,
      "text": "of the class it belongs to the class itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 433435.0,
      "end_time": 434675.0,
      "text": "So let me explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 434675.0,
      "end_time": 437320.0,
      "text": "Whenever we&#39;re dragging on EnemyHealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 437320.0,
      "end_time": 439885.0,
      "text": "or PlayerHealth or PlayerMovement on to an object"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 439885.0,
      "end_time": 442277.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re creating an instance of that class"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 442278.0,
      "end_time": 444278.0,
      "text": "and applying it to the game object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 444278.0,
      "end_time": 446278.0,
      "text": "so they are all instances of a class."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 447358.0,
      "end_time": 449358.0,
      "text": "And so all of the variables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 449358.0,
      "end_time": 451358.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re instance variables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 451358.0,
      "end_time": 455193.0,
      "text": "each enemy has it&#39;s own health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 455193.0,
      "end_time": 458217.0,
      "text": "each player has it&#39;s own speed, etcetera."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 458218.0,
      "end_time": 462237.0,
      "text": "Static variables do not belong to an instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 462237.0,
      "end_time": 464786.0,
      "text": "they belong to the class itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 464786.0,
      "end_time": 466786.0,
      "text": "So what that means is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 466786.0,
      "end_time": 469769.0,
      "text": "in order to reference the score there"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 470417.0,
      "end_time": 474941.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t need to go ScoreManager variable"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 474941.0,
      "end_time": 479751.0,
      "text": "GetComponent ScoreManager then use it, we just say"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 479751.0,
      "end_time": 483383.0,
      "text": "ScoreManager type . score."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 483923.0,
      "end_time": 486314.0,
      "text": "So we don&#39;t need to create a variable to use it"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 486314.0,
      "end_time": 489496.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re just going to use it through the type itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 489496.0,
      "end_time": 492885.0,
      "text": "So it only effectively exists in one place"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 492886.0,
      "end_time": 494886.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not going to address a bunch of instances where"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 494886.0,
      "end_time": 497868.0,
      "text": "this exists, we&#39;re changing it in 1 place."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 497868.0,
      "end_time": 499868.0,
      "text": "We could still have multiple"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 499868.0,
      "end_time": 501868.0,
      "text": "instance of ScoreManager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 501868.0,
      "end_time": 503868.0,
      "text": "we could drag multiple ones on to"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 503868.0,
      "end_time": 507704.0,
      "text": "a game object, on to different game objects, doesn&#39;t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 507704.0,
      "end_time": 510567.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not going to, because that would break everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 510567.0,
      "end_time": 514894.0,
      "text": "But if we did all of them would share the same score."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 514894.0,
      "end_time": 516894.0,
      "text": "because it belongs to the type"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 516894.0,
      "end_time": 518894.0,
      "text": "not to the instance."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 518894.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "So the next thing is we need a reference to our Text component."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 523544.0,
      "text": "In awake we&#39;re going to setup that reference"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 523544.0,
      "end_time": 525127.0,
      "text": "to the text component."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 525127.0,
      "end_time": 527127.0,
      "text": "Then we need to reset the score"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 527127.0,
      "end_time": 529127.0,
      "text": "because if we die we want"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 529127.0,
      "end_time": 531127.0,
      "text": "the game to reset, so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 531127.0,
      "end_time": 533127.0,
      "text": "we need to set the score back to 0."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 533127.0,
      "end_time": 535127.0,
      "text": "And in our update function"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 535127.0,
      "end_time": 539122.0,
      "text": "what we&#39;re doing there, the text.text is"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 539122.0,
      "end_time": 541824.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re changing the text property"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 541825.0,
      "end_time": 543825.0,
      "text": "of the text component."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 543825.0,
      "end_time": 545825.0,
      "text": "Okay, so the text component that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 545825.0,
      "end_time": 550297.0,
      "text": "that string that we said Score: 0,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 550297.0,
      "end_time": 553453.0,
      "text": "that was the Score text,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 553453.0,
      "end_time": 556699.0,
      "text": "that was the text property of the component."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 556699.0,
      "end_time": 559890.0,
      "text": "So what we&#39;re doing is we&#39;re setting that"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 559890.0,
      "end_time": 561890.0,
      "text": "to a completely new string, we&#39;re not changing that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 561890.0,
      "end_time": 564167.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re just setting it completely afresh."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 564167.0,
      "end_time": 567250.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re changing it to Score:"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 567250.0,
      "end_time": 569760.0,
      "text": "and then that number will be the score."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 570932.0,
      "end_time": 572932.0,
      "text": "So very simply that&#39;s our ScoreManager and"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 572932.0,
      "end_time": 574932.0,
      "text": "if you happen to save it it&#39;ll ask you to convert"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 574932.0,
      "end_time": 576932.0,
      "text": "the line endings, it&#39;s no big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 577300.0,
      "end_time": 580934.0,
      "text": "Okay, we&#39;ll need to continue scoring points"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 580934.0,
      "end_time": 582934.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to select my"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 582934.0,
      "end_time": 584934.0,
      "text": "Zombunny in the hierarchy"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 584934.0,
      "end_time": 588808.0,
      "text": "and locate the EnemyHealth script."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 588808.0,
      "end_time": 591484.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re going to open the EnemyHealth script."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 592715.0,
      "end_time": 595405.0,
      "text": "and have a look down at the very bottom"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 595405.0,
      "end_time": 598476.0,
      "text": "at the StartSinging function."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 598476.0,
      "end_time": 601299.0,
      "text": "James mentioned the public static"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 601299.0,
      "end_time": 603299.0,
      "text": "integer score earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 603299.0,
      "end_time": 605299.0,
      "text": "he promised you very kindly that you could"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 605299.0,
      "end_time": 607299.0,
      "text": "indeed say the name of"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 607299.0,
      "end_time": 611260.0,
      "text": "the class, ScoreManager.score,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 611270.0,
      "end_time": 613270.0,
      "text": "so without saying GetComponent"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 613270.0,
      "end_time": 616373.0,
      "text": "or create an instance of the script, assign to this part of the script"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 616373.0,
      "end_time": 620383.0,
      "text": "we can very simply just say ScoreManager.score."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 620383.0,
      "end_time": 622383.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to re-enable that by deleting"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 622383.0,
      "end_time": 624951.0,
      "text": "the 2 // comments."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 624951.0,
      "end_time": 627503.0,
      "text": "And what we&#39;re doing there is adding to it"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 627503.0,
      "end_time": 630622.0,
      "text": "the value of ScoreValue."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 630622.0,
      "end_time": 636992.0,
      "text": "So scoreValue within this particular script is"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 636992.0,
      "end_time": 639690.0,
      "text": "a public variable that we can change."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 639691.0,
      "end_time": 644728.0,
      "text": "This enemy has a value of 10 that when you kill it you get 10 points."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 644728.0,
      "end_time": 646728.0,
      "text": "This way we can apply this"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 646728.0,
      "end_time": 648728.0,
      "text": "EnemyHealth script to different enemies"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 648728.0,
      "end_time": 650424.0,
      "text": "and have different score values."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 650424.0,
      "end_time": 652424.0,
      "text": "So if you wanted to make the"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 652424.0,
      "end_time": 654424.0,
      "text": "killing the elephant worth a lot then you could"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 654424.0,
      "end_time": 656424.0,
      "text": "change that value, you don&#39;t need to go in to the"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 656424.0,
      "end_time": 658424.0,
      "text": "script and change it, it&#39;s a public value"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 658424.0,
      "end_time": 660424.0,
      "text": "so it appears in the inspector."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 660424.0,
      "end_time": 663896.0,
      "text": "I just want to make a quick point about static variables."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 663897.0,
      "end_time": 667705.0,
      "text": "So you know it&#39;s a lot easier to do it with static there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 667705.0,
      "end_time": 670410.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t have to create an instance variable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 670410.0,
      "end_time": 672410.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t have to assign it in awake"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 672410.0,
      "end_time": 674653.0,
      "text": "and then use it, we just used it just like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 674653.0,
      "end_time": 677206.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t we use it for everything like that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 677206.0,
      "end_time": 678700.0,
      "text": "That would be so much easier?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 678700.0,
      "end_time": 682147.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because we have multiple enemies"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 682147.0,
      "end_time": 684147.0,
      "text": "and if we wanted multiple players then"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 684147.0,
      "end_time": 685660.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d have more of those as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 685660.0,
      "end_time": 687660.0,
      "text": "So if we wanted to change the health"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 687660.0,
      "end_time": 690848.0,
      "text": "of one player all of the player&#39;s health would change."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 690848.0,
      "end_time": 692848.0,
      "text": "So we can&#39;t do it most of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 692848.0,
      "end_time": 694848.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just very specific circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 694848.0,
      "end_time": 696848.0,
      "text": "where you&#39;d only have one score"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 696848.0,
      "end_time": 698848.0,
      "text": "so we can make that static"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 698848.0,
      "end_time": 700848.0,
      "text": "to make it easier for ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 700848.0,
      "end_time": 702848.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to save this, it&#39;s going to ask you"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 702848.0,
      "end_time": 705865.0,
      "text": "to convert line endings, just choose Convert."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 705865.0,
      "end_time": 707865.0,
      "text": "This project was made on PC and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 707865.0,
      "end_time": 709865.0,
      "text": "moved between PC and Mac so the files"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 709865.0,
      "end_time": 711865.0,
      "text": "get confused but it&#39;s no big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 712554.0,
      "end_time": 714554.0,
      "text": "So we should now go ahead and try it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 714554.0,
      "end_time": 716554.0,
      "text": "So if you save your scene and press play"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 716554.0,
      "end_time": 718554.0,
      "text": "at the top of the interface."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 721736.0,
      "end_time": 725500.0,
      "text": "There we go, 10 points for a Zombunny."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 725693.0,
      "end_time": 729540.0,
      "text": "A very important point to make right now about prefabs"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 729540.0,
      "end_time": 732343.0,
      "text": "is that they are incredibly useful when you want to"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 732343.0,
      "end_time": 734343.0,
      "text": "spawn more than one object."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 734343.0,
      "end_time": 736343.0,
      "text": "So some people might use if for rockets in a game"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 736343.0,
      "end_time": 738737.0,
      "text": "and you might use it for enemy spawning in a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 738737.0,
      "end_time": 740737.0,
      "text": "You can use it for really anything you want to"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 741621.0,
      "end_time": 743621.0,
      "text": "But we want to use that for our enemies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 743621.0,
      "end_time": 745129.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s going to be 3 types of enemy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 745129.0,
      "end_time": 748920.0,
      "text": "and you guys have gone and created that first enemy."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 748920.0,
      "end_time": 750920.0,
      "text": "What we don&#39;t want is just the enemy to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 750920.0,
      "end_time": 752920.0,
      "text": "sat next to the player when the game starts."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 752920.0,
      "end_time": 756493.0,
      "text": "So what we need to do is to save him as a prefab."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 756494.0,
      "end_time": 758494.0,
      "text": "So everybody make sure you&#39;ve stopped play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 758494.0,
      "end_time": 762573.0,
      "text": "so play is no longer on, it should be black at the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 762573.0,
      "end_time": 764101.0,
      "text": "No more blue buttons."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 764101.0,
      "end_time": 765620.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re going to do is to select our"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 765620.0,
      "end_time": 767998.0,
      "text": "Prefabs folder in the project"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 767998.0,
      "end_time": 770875.0,
      "text": "and then grab the Zombunny in the hierarchy"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 770875.0,
      "end_time": 773288.0,
      "text": "and drag and drop it in to the project panel"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 773288.0,
      "end_time": 775288.0,
      "text": "either in the empty space or drop it on"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 775288.0,
      "end_time": 776921.0,
      "text": "to the Prefabs folder."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 777460.0,
      "end_time": 779936.0,
      "text": "Both of those will create the same effect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 779936.0,
      "end_time": 781936.0,
      "text": "you will get a Zombunny prefab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 781936.0,
      "end_time": 783936.0,
      "text": "which looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 785400.0,
      "end_time": 787400.0,
      "text": "And you will have all of the same settings"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 787400.0,
      "end_time": 789400.0,
      "text": "that you had on the version that&#39;s in the scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 790106.0,
      "end_time": 792106.0,
      "text": "So that version in the scene now belongs"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 792106.0,
      "end_time": 794106.0,
      "text": "to that prefab parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 794106.0,
      "end_time": 796106.0,
      "text": "And even if we delete the version in"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 796106.0,
      "end_time": 798314.0,
      "text": "the scene, in the hierarchy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 798314.0,
      "end_time": 800831.0,
      "text": "then the version in the project is saved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 800831.0,
      "end_time": 802191.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s very crucial."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 803259.0,
      "end_time": 805259.0,
      "text": "Everybody check that you&#39;ve got your Zombunny"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 805259.0,
      "end_time": 807630.0,
      "text": "in the project, it&#39;s very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 807630.0,
      "end_time": 810250.0,
      "text": "Then in the hierarchy we want to get rid of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 810250.0,
      "end_time": 811818.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;m going to select it there and"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 811818.0,
      "end_time": 813818.0,
      "text": "on Mac Command Backspace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 813818.0,
      "end_time": 815818.0,
      "text": "on PC just the delete key."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 815818.0,
      "end_time": 817818.0,
      "text": "Remove it from the scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 817818.0,
      "end_time": 820812.0,
      "text": "And then save your scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 820812.0,
      "end_time": 822812.0,
      "text": "Switch off 2D mode and double click the"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 822812.0,
      "end_time": 824812.0,
      "text": "player to zoom back in to the action"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 824812.0,
      "end_time": 826812.0,
      "text": "so you can see the player."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 827651.0,
      "end_time": 830873.0,
      "text": "Okay, so that is the end of phase 8."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 830874.0,
      "end_time": 833000.0,
      "text": "Subtitles by the Amara.org community"
    }
  ]
}